177
0:07:33.33,000 --> 0:07:36,000
It wouldn't eat. It wouldn't sleep. It wouldn't have sex.

178
0:07:36.33,000 --> 0:07:38,000
It wouldn't do anything but press this bar.

179
0:07:38.33,000 --> 0:07:4,000
So they assumed

180
0:07:40.33,000 --> 0:07:42,000
this must be, you know, the brain's orgasmatron.

181
0:07:42.33,000 --> 0:07:44,000
It turned out that it wasn't,

182
0:07:44.33,000 --> 0:07:46,000
