183
0:07:46.33,000 --> 0:07:48,000
a system of wanting.

184
0:07:48.33,000 --> 0:07:51,000
It gives objects what's called incentive salience.

185
0:07:51.33,000 --> 0:07:53,000
It makes something look so attractive

186
0:07:53.33,000 --> 0:07:55,000
that you just have to go after it.

187
0:07:55.33,000 --> 0:07:57,000
That's something different

188
0:07:57.33,000 --> 0:08:,000
from the system that is the pleasure system,

189
0:08:00.33,000 --> 0:08:02,000
which simply says, "I like this."

190
0:08:02.33,000 --> 0:08:04,000
The pleasure system, as you see,

191
0:08:04.33,000 --> 0:08:07,000
which is the internal opiates, there is a hormone oxytocin,

192
0:08:07.33,000 --> 0:08:09,000
is widely spread throughout the brain.

193
0:08:09.33,000 --> 0:08:11,000
Dopamine system, the wanting system,

194
0:08:11.33,000 --> 0:08:13,000
is much more centralized.

195
0:08:13.33,000 --> 0:08:16,000
